Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface ForwardRelation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotatedElement, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Feature, IdentifiedElement, Member, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Relation, Term
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ForwardRelationImpl
    public interface ForwardRelation
extends Relation
    A representation of the model object 'Forward Relation'. ForwardRelation is a relation that is defined along side a relation entity, whose domain is the source of the relation entity, and whose range is the target of the relation entity. A forward relation has DL semantics that are specified by the boolean flags of its relation entity.

    The following features are supported:

    • Relation Entity
